23:02.590 --> 23:04.759
♪ Got a nice style
And your girls do, too ♪

23:04.968 --> 23:07.304
♪ See, we just wanna party
Have a little fun ♪

23:07.470 --> 23:10.098
♪ You ain't gotta be ashamed
Bad girls have fun ♪

23:10.765 --> 23:13.184
♪ I like them bad
